Package net.fabricmc.fabric.api.dimension.v1

Class FabricDimensionType

java.lang.Object
net.minecraft.world.dimension.DimensionType
net.fabricmc.fabric.api.dimension.v1.FabricDimensionType
All Implemented Interfaces:
net.minecraft.util.dynamic.DynamicSerializable
public final class FabricDimensionType
extends net.minecraft.world.dimension.DimensionType
An extended version of DimensionType with automatic raw id management and default placement settings. FabricDimensionType instances are constructed and registered through a FabricDimensionType.Builder.
See Also:
builder(), getDefaultPlacement(), getDesiredRawId()

    • getRawId

      public int getRawId()
      Return the current raw id for this dimension type.

      The returned id is guaranteed to be unique and persistent in a save, as well as synchronized between a server and its connected clients. It may change when connecting to a different server or opening a new save.
